M = coker vars S;
L = stronglyLinearStrand(M)--should give the Koszul complex, and the following 5 assertions check that it does.
assert(numcols basis HH_0 L == 1)
assert(HH_1 L == 0)
assert(HH_2 L == 0)
assert(HH_3 L == 0)
assert(HH_4 L == 0)
